title: Mountain Landscape
description: A serene landscape featuring two prominent mountains, one with a snow-capped peak. The mountains are surrounded by a calm body of water, reflecting the clear blue sky above. The foreground includes a grassy area leading to the water's edge, while the background showcases the rugged terrain of the mountains.

title: Penguins on Ice
description: A group of penguins standing on a large piece of ice, with a clear blue sky in the background. The ice appears to be floating, and the penguins are in various poses, some looking around while others are standing still.
